criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients older than 18 years of age;

          -  Irrespective of gender;

          -  Symptomatic patients of liver abscess confirmed with radiology imaging, either by
             ultrasonography or computed tomography scan.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients <18 years old;

          -  Pregnancy at presentation.
